I tried this today; I didn't have any problems printing out an IndexedSlices object, or even a tensor and an IndexedSlices together (the IndexedSlices is converted to a tensor before printing). So I would suppose this is fixed in the meantime; feel free to reopen with more information if it still doesn't work for you.
